{"tid":1517550,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我地成功在望","createTime":"2019-08-30T03:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T09:59:32.000Z","uid":152455,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"55ac53e6bc0b4266a6d39657c283750016510c64","tid":1517550,"uid":152455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:04:30.000Z","msg":"文攻武嚇<br />\n<br />\n文：<br />\n一晚捉晒所有學運領袖，希望831少d人<br />\n實質對家都知呢班人唔係大台，只係佢都冇晒辦法，唯有試下捉晒呢d名人睇下有冇效果，用黎嚇鬼咁解，但反效果係幫習慣失憶既香港keep住團火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n武：<br />\n777死都唔查警察，佢講明怕佢地嬲嬲唔開心，佢地一唔開心再冇人會鎮壓到香港人，咁老解愛黎做咩架？就算出駛鬼由大陸落黎咩？佢當註港個幾千人廢架？冇錯，佢地只係擺係度裝飾，又係嚇鬼用，實際作用係零<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n宜家亂9咁拉人，冒求拉得幾多得幾多係佢最後可以用既武牌，正所謂消滅提出問題既人不嬲都係中共作風。商場、教育界、國泰既白色恐怖係佢地最後一隻可以用既文牌。<br />\n<br />\n所有野打橫黎唔講道理，因為已經冇撚晒計又就到70大壽急到瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只要用埋呢兩隻牌都冇效都冇咩野可以用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以香港人宜家更加要團結到底！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過除非我高估左對家智商，到宜家都覺得有大台操控，咁我地只係對住個豬咁蠢既敵人，</span></span>全世界智商最高既香港人對豬敵人，想唔贏都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">不過幾豬都唔可以輕敵</span></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e04759adae877f648b0a0043a51476dd788fb802","tid":1517550,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:04:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mhik2fq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhik2fq.gif&h=7b54c7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8ubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=6498ebd1\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8ubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=0d98be7d\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8ubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=fa9853b8\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"d9a6d2c926f942c4a9ab7b5687a22ab846d3acc8","tid":1517550,"uid":152455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:14:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1308e7e1b75113ccb13f87cb9f939357a33711b2","tid":1517550,"uid":175715,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:15:57.000Z","msg":"係唔係成功在望 我唔太夠膽落定論<br />\n但肯定既係我地仲未贏<br />\n要各位手足堅持先會贏到"},{"pid":"42c0611f0c54fd2797d9764334e902a20a4ad0ec","tid":1517550,"uid":152976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:19:35.000Z","msg":"0:5 其實點樣成功在望<br />\n唔係話鼓吹失敗 但唔可以過份悲觀嘅同時亦都唔可以過份樂觀<br />\n所以認同你最後講唔可以輕敵<br />\n大家加油!"},{"pid":"87d14f9d15665e210d61a7b09dce7701bcabd4ca","tid":1517550,"uid":152455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:22:24.000Z","msg":"鼓勵下大家，我相信呢d都係事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"816bca6cda7730cb4c14afa5089e66ec559585e1","tid":1517550,"uid":152584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:24:14.000Z","msg":"堅持信念 可能要捱多3個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ec0fb4cebcc225452f4ddaaf8d4eeaf6e374878","tid":1517550,"uid":139173,"like":0,"di